title: The Perfect Hot Dog With Homemade Buns feat. Roy Choi
description:
Making the perfect hot dog starts by making the perfect hot dog bun, I'm talking that homemade stuff. You know how I am. Not to mention our special guest Roy Choi from The Chef Show on Netflix walking us through the famed hot dog from Best Friend at Park MGM in Las Vegas... hot dogs will never be the same.
